name: 20 Years of SF Dance Music J-Kind Audio NFT
description: Nearly everyone who has regularly gone out in San Francisco over the last twenty years has seen, heard, and been moved by waves of change in some ways very different from all the others that came before. 5 top SF DJs and Musicians are combining forces for a collective ensemble release with DIGIFIZZY. Taking those tunes to the digi base. J-KIND is a DJ/Producer residing in San Francisco Bay Area of California. His diverse and eclectic style transcends many genres and is currently focused on his burning passion for techno.
